{"word":"καταγράφω","slug":"καταγράφω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταγράφω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ψω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to scratch away, lacerate</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to engrave, inscribe</i>, <el>νόμους</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to paint over</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to fill</i> tablets <i>with writing</i> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to write down, register, record</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}